ating railway and surrounding road network, as well as difficulty in accessing the site due to the topography with 60% of the site located on an elevated fill embankment with slopes up to 38°. The critical concern to ensure there would be no disruption to the railway&#x27;s normal operation presented the biggest challenge to this project.</p>','2025-06-02 03:52:05.605000','2025-07-07 07:22:28.053000',NULL,8,36,'en',29.00),(187,'l54temurqnied2a0501x5s84','Lantau and Airport Railway Siu Ho Wan Depot, Phase I (MTRC Contract No. 518)','Lantau and Airport Railway Siu Ho Wan Depot, Phase I','Mass Transit Railway Corporation','01 January 1995 - 31 May 1998','<p>This was one of the projects of the Airport Core Programme therefore timely completion of the works was critical. The main depot building completion was paramount for the success of the project.</p><p>As there was no land access to the site for this multi-discipline project, careful consideration had to be given to procurement, delivery, and storage of materials.</p><p>The completion of the North Lantau Expressway bridge and associated access roads and embankments within a 3 month period exemplified the project team&#x27;s teamwork &amp; determination to complete the works on time.</p>','2025-06-02 03:53:11.025000','2025-07-07 07:22:28.380000',NULL,8,36,'en',30.00),(189,'b7wyl78n2s4i1q64zgfm26zy','大屿山与机场铁路小蚝湾车厂第一期 (地下铁路 合约编号：518)','大屿山与机场铁路小蚝湾车厂第一期','地下铁路公司','1995 年 01 月 01 日 - 1998 年 05 月 31 日','<p>本工程为新机场核心工程之一部份，所以准时完成工程十分重要。车厂主楼能够准时完工是本次成功的重要因素。</p><p>由于项目包括多种不同类别之工程，而又没有陆路可以直达工地，材料采购、运送、储存均需事前策划完善。</p><p>本工程北大屿山快速公路桥梁及有关道路和路堤工程均能于三个月内完成，反映出工程队伍之合作精神及准时完成工程之决心。</p>','2025-06-02 03:53:41.265000','2025-07-07 07:22:25.455000',NULL,8,36,'zh-CN',30.00),(191,'qsg4bq0eag2blua3r69en46d','大嶼山與機場鐵路小蚝灣車廠第一期 (香港鐵路有限公司)','大嶼山與機場鐵路小蚝灣車廠第一期','地下鐵路 合約編號：518','1995 年 01 月 01 日 - 1998 年 05 月 31 日','<p>本工程爲新機場核心工程之一部份，所以準時完成工程十分重要。車廠主樓能夠準時完工是本次成功的重要因素。</p><p>由於項目包括多種不同類別之工程，而又沒有陸路可以直達工地，材料採購、運送、儲存均需事前策劃完善。</p><p>本工程北大嶼山快速公路橋樑及有關道路和路堤工程均能於三個月內完成，反映出工程隊伍之合作精神及準時完成工程之決心。</p>','2025-06-02 03:54:18.966000','2025-07-07 07:22:24.884000',NULL,8,36,'zh-Hant-HK',30.00),(193,'skmq8qcymiq67fxdthzqyt4e','中環隧道 (大嶼山及機場鐵路 合約編號：501A)','中環隧道','地下鐵路有限公司','1994 年 12 月 05 日 - 1998 年 03 月 31 日','<p>為配合機場快綫工程，港鐵於香港站興建一條用以接駁中環地鐵站的行人隧道。工程的施工地段位於香港聯合交易所及交通繁忙的街道下，340米長的隧道位於地面以下18米深，寬度由10米至34米不等。</p>','2025-06-02 03:55:12.903000','2025-07-07 07:22:26.004000',NULL,8,36,'zh-Hant-HK',31.00),(195,'d12m2wpbnvbr22he624w3xdi','大嶼山及機場鐵路九龍南隧道及輔助樓房 (合約編號：503B)','大嶼山及機場鐵路九龍南隧道及輔助樓房','香港鐵路有限公司','1994 年 11 月 01 日 - 1998 年 02 月 28 日','<p>這工程是機場快線的其中一段，工程包括在西九沉管式隧道和新九龍站之間建造機房大樓及隧道。</p><br/><p>工程項目包括：</p><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>建造截水牆</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>大型開挖作隧道興建</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>鑽孔樁工程</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>安裝防洪閘和在水底安裝海水引進 /出PC裝置</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>相關的渠務及路面配套</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>附屬建築物</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>裝飾面及面板</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>環境美化</li></ul>','2025-06-02 03:56:03.378000','2025-07-07 07:22:26.835000',NULL,8,36,'zh-Hant-HK',32.00),(197,'vleeuoczzrijqa4unls2vumx','中环隧道 (大屿山及机场铁路 合约编号：501A)','中环隧道','地下铁路有限公司','1994 年 12 月 05 日 - 1998 年 03 月 31 日','<p>为配合机场快线工程，港铁于香港站兴建一条用以接驳中环地铁站的行人隧道。工程的施工地段位于香港联合交易所及交通繁忙的街道下，340米长的隧道位于地面以下18米深，宽度由10米至34米不等。</p>','2025-06-02 03:57:47.107000','2025-07-07 07:22:24.603000',NULL,8,36,'zh-CN',31.00),(199,'wxfhz7c9anstft9gzd2zfuf9','Central Subway (Lantau and Airport Railway Contract No. 501A)','Central Subway','Mass Transit Railway Corporation Limited','05 December 1994 - 31 March 1998','<p>MTRC developed a passenger subway to connect the Central Station and the Hong Kong Station the Airport Express Line.</p><p>The project, located beneath heavily trafficked streets and under the Hong Kong Stock Exchange, is a 340m-long subway varying in width between 10m and 34m, and extends to a depth of 18m below ground level.</p>','2025-06-02 03:58:21.899000','2025-07-07 07:22:27.873000',NULL,8,36,'en',31.00),(201,'mk9ip9j22cup3glbfai8zl0g','Lantau and Airport Railway Kowloon South Tunnels and Ancillary Building (MTRC Contract No.503B)','Lantau and Airport Railway Kowloon South Tunnels and Ancillary Building','Mass Transit Railway Corporation','01 November 1994 - 28 February 1998','<p>This project, which forms part of the overall scheme for the Lantau and Airport Railway Link between the Western Immersed Tube and the new Kowloon Station, involves the construction of plant buildings and tunnels.</p><br/><p>The project consisted of:</p><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>Construction of diaphragm walls</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>Large open cut excavation to construct the tunnel sections</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>Bored piling works</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>Installation of floodgates and positioning of seawater intake/outfall p c units underwater</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>Associated drainage and access roads</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>Ancillary building</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>Architectural; finishes and cladding</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>landscaping</li></ul>','2025-06-02 03:59:42.023000','2025-07-07 07:22:27.943000',NULL,8,36,'en',32.00),(204,'lk8dpobeddsc41yfastuybxd','大屿山及机场铁路九龙南隧道及辅助楼房 (合约编号：503B)','大屿山及机场铁路九龙南隧道及辅助楼房','地下铁路公司','1994 年 11 月 01 日 - 1998 年 02 月 28 日','<p>这工程是机场快线的其中一段，工程包括在西九沈管式隧道和新九龙站之间建造机房大楼及隧道。</p><br/><p>工程项目包括：</p><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>建造截水墙</li></ul><ul class=