-07 07:22:27.611000',8,36,'zh-Hant-HK',28.00),(397,'l3ssvk9swok10djttdy1hcvm','Addition and Alteration to station facilities at Hung Hom Station (Contract No. KA W835','Addition and Alteration to station facilities at Hung Hom Station','MTR Corporation Limited','04 April 2007 - 22 December 2009','<p>The major scope of this project is to modify the existing Hung Hom Station to cater for the operation of Kowloon Southern Link. The works consist of :</p><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>Demolition of existing staircase, plant rooms and lift shaft</li><li>Modification of existing plant rooms</li><li>Reconfiguration of new 4 numbers of escalator control room (ECR).</li><li>Replacement / Provision of platform ceiling with lighting enhancement</li><li>Replace / Provide new signage including supply and install new platform header board sign along the platforms.</li><li>Construct new generator room</li><li>Fitting-out works</li></ul>','2025-06-02 02:32:49.318000','2025-07-07 07:22:27.371000','2025-07-07 07:22:27.646000',8,36,'en',13.00),(398,'febtq2joiswcanh766qfzshu','康樂園隔音措施 (合約編號：1/ICP/2000)','康樂園隔音措施','九廣鐵路公司','2000 年 11 月 01 日 - 2001 年 07 月 07 日','<p>由於施工時間在列車服務期間進行，必須先設置一個欄分隔開現有的路軌和工作區。此外，豎立垂直的鋼柱及安裝隔音板須特別小心，以確保沒有任何物件誤落路軌，及沒有任何人能觸及在2.75米高的高電壓設備的起重操作。</p><br/><p>由於工作區有進出限制，令運送混凝土出現困難，由康樂園路經過400米長水下澆注管把混凝土送住地盤南端作基腳及豎立構件之用極具挑戰。</p><br/><p>地盤與康樂園十分接近，部分裝卸貨區的道路亦屬康樂園範圍。工程需得到康樂園管理處對路面使用的批准及承諾處理施工過程中的任何投訴。最後工程在沒有任何投訴及與康樂園管理處友好合作關係下順利完成。</p>','2025-06-02 02:56:16.155000','2025-07-07 07:22:27.487000','2025-07-07 07:22:27.661000',8,36,'zh-Hant-HK',18.00),(399,'kgoxlgtbk2qlukc7cxo6bu8s','灣仔站利東街行人隧道及出入口改善工程 (合約編號 C6593-13C)','灣仔站利東街行人隧道及出入口改善工程','香港鐵路有限公司','2014 年 04 月 14 日 - 2017 年 07 月 18 日','<p>為提升車站設施及配合市區重建局的重建項目，並且改善灣仔南北行人設施的連繫，為行人及港鐵乘客提供直接、方便、安全及舒適的通道橫過莊士敦道，港鐵公司決定進行灣仔站利東街行人隧道工程。長約100米的利東街行人隧道途經修頓遊樂場及莊士敦道地底，接駁港鐵灣仔站大堂非付款區的西面及市區重建局於利東街的重建項目的商場地庫。隧道工程以明挖回填方法建造，工程期間，一段莊士敦道進行臨時的交通安排，為確保道路行車及電車維持運作，現有電車軌道底需進行土力加固以便挖掘。此外，工程還同時進行修頓運動場的優化工程，包括重鋪籃球場地墊、更換休憩設施等。</p>','2025-06-02 01:26:01.354000','2025-07-07 07:22:27.457000','2025-07-07 07:22:27.719000',8,36,'zh-Hant-HK',3.00),(400,'hl90lvymsnvvhcynimq12vsd',' Ngau Tam Mei to Tai Kong Po Tunnels (Express Rail Link - Contract No. 824)','Ngau Tam Mei to Tai Kong Po Tunnels','MTR Corporation Limited','16 August 2010 - 31 May 2017','<p>XRL Contract 824 was one of the XRL tunnel contracts. The tunnel runs beneath the natural terrain of Lam Tsuen Country Park between Ngau Tam Mei in the north and Tai Kong Po in the south.  Drill-and-blast method was adopted for excavating the approximately 2.6 km tunnel. The rock nature is mainly volcanic tuff.</p><p>A temporary circular shaft was constructed at Tai Kong Po for mucking out and material delivery.  Two permanent shafts were subsequently constructed at both ends of the tunnels.  Most of the tunnel&#x27;s track was run on twin bore single track. These tunnels had an internal span of 7.8 m and an internal height of 7.6 m.  The project included the construction of a Crossover Cavern with an internal span of 22.2 m (resulting in an external span of circa 25 m), an internal height of 15.0 m and a length of 115 m. The cavern is 25 m away from the Ngau Tam Mei Shaft.  The existing design requires the construction of twin bore, single track running tunnels with overhead ventilation duct between the Ngau Tam Mei Shaft and the cavern to facilitate construction. This XRL Contract 824 also included the construction of a ventilation building at Ngau Tam Mei and an emergency access point at Tai Kong Po.</p><p>In line with the construction of the tunnels, there were also some external works associated with this contract which included widening of Chi Ho Road and Kong Tai Road, miscellaneous external works such as paving, landscaping, utilities works, earth works, ELS, piling / geotechnical works etc.</p>','2025-06-01 09:19:25.289000','2025-07-07 07:22:27.519000','2025-07-07 07:22:27.777000',8,36,'en',9.00),(401,'mtt7ix08upnx0xkmn4pkio7b','Trackwork, 